stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> PLAN_READY
  PLAN_READY --> OPERATOR_OPENING: executor opens root
  OPERATOR_OPENING --> CHILD_READING: child cursor opened
  CHILD_READING --> ROW_LOCK_WAIT: storage current read waits
  ROW_LOCK_WAIT --> CHILD_READING: granted and relocated
  CHILD_READING --> MEMORY_HELD: operator buffers rows
  MEMORY_HELD --> SPILLING: memory quota exceeded
  SPILLING --> TEMP_IO: acquire spill file lock
  TEMP_IO --> MEMORY_HELD: run written or merged
  MEMORY_HELD --> RESULT_EMITTING: output row ready
  RESULT_EMITTING --> CHILD_READING: need more rows
  RESULT_EMITTING --> CLOSING: no more rows
  CLOSING --> RELEASED: guards close
  RELEASED --> [*]

  OPERATOR_OPENING --> FAILED: open error
  CHILD_READING --> FAILED: child error
  SPILLING --> FAILED: temp IO error
  FAILED --> CLOSING: cleanup
